Message:
Hi there! 

I am a Software Engineer for Optum Technology in Spencer Dock and I am currently looking for accommodation in Dublin. I am interested in renting this lovely apartment! 

Please let me know if viewings are available at this time. I would be available to move in as soon as the apartment is available. 

I can provide a glowing reference from a former college professor of mine in addition to a work reference and a previous landlord reference. I can also provide a payslip as proof of funds. 

Thank you for your time, I look forward to hearing from you soon. 

Kindest Regards, 
Gerald Wogan.
